          <source>is a wide-character version of <ph id="ph1">`_splitpath`</ph>; the arguments to <ph id="ph2">`_wsplitpath`</ph> are wide-character strings.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="121" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
